We further questioned about the fact of whether such an inhomogeneous
distribution could be described by a fractal. We numerically computed
the limit
_r  N(r) r^d ,where  finding the value of 
where the limit exists. This is the usual definition of a fractal dimension
. Some results are sumarized in Figure 3.




